snippet.title: Minion Masters 2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
Masters! 
Get ready to discover a new version of the game on PC, Xbox, and soon on Android! You can pre-register here: 
--------------------
An addictive fast-paced hybrid of Card games & Tower-Defense. Play 1v1 - or bring a friend for 2v2 - and engage in epic online multiplayer battles full of innovative strategy and awesome plays! 
--------------------
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/489520/Minion_Masters/
Xbox Store: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/Minion-Masters/9NRPPQHL2MZM
--------------------
Find out more:
https://www.minionmastersthegame.com/ 

Follow Minion Masters: 
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/MinionMasters/
Discord: https://discord.gg/minionmasters
Twitter (X): https://twitter.com/minion_masters
